room_title: Escape room "Sweet Dreams" by Epic Escape Game in Denver
room_description: Sweet Dreams is Englewood’s newest, hippest bakery. Within just weeks of opening, word of their irresistible desserts has spread throughout the city and they’ve amassed a devoted, almost obsessive following. As a Health Inspector, you receive an anonymous tip that something unusual is going on in the Sweet Dreams kitchen. You show up to find that the popular eatery is eerily empty, and you hear the door shut and lock behind you.
